		<title>水果有哪些作用和功效（常见水果的作用和功效）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/6549.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2023 08:03:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[富含]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[有助于]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[研讨]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=6549</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[苹果有益于大脑 研讨发现：苹果中富含的抗氧化剂槲皮素，能改进神经系统的全体健康状况。美国康奈尔大学的研讨者则发 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">苹果有益于大脑</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/85feb43ec686a4bf42a8eadd59a17555.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">研讨发现：苹果中富含的抗氧化剂槲皮素，能改进神经系统的全体健康状况。美国康奈尔大学的研讨者则发现，苹果有助于维护神经细胞免受氧化应激反响，降低了大家患上认知障碍症的风险。</p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">香蕉防止心脏病</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a6fbf1e8412e34ad5b03fbd8e6a77e19.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">香蕉中所富含的膳食纤维、钾元素、维生素C和维生素B6协同作业，能保证心脏处于最优的作业状况。</p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">葡萄有助于焚烧脂肪</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/cdaf6000a317afaf34b74371e26ba406.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">葡萄中富含的白藜芦醇，焚烧脂肪的效果特别好。美国佐治亚大学的研讨者发现：白藜芦醇能致使脂肪细胞的分化速度比正常速度快出2.46倍。</p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">橙子能减轻皱纹</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e1c2a906cd99ab1821eb80fdb653539f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">橙子中丰富的维C有助于反转阳光和污染导致的肌肤损害，削减皱纹，进步肌肤的全体质地。</p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">梨能防止癌症</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/621bb5113fef0e9eda1412c328e46928.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨中富含的膳食纤维要比其他水果都要多，它有助于结肠中致癌物质的排出，然后降低大家患上结肠癌的风险。此外，它还富含根皮素这种类黄酮，能按捺黑色素瘤、淋巴癌、肝癌和结肠癌细胞的成长。</p>
    </div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
